<p><Link to="/source/prpg_core_rulebook">PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 68</Link> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-1" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-1" aria-label="Back to reference C-1">↩</InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-2" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-2" aria-label="Back to reference C-2">↩<sup>2</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-3" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-3" aria-label="Back to reference C-3">↩<sup>3</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-4" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-4" aria-label="Back to reference C-4">↩<sup>4</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-5" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-5" aria-label="Back to reference C-5">↩<sup>5</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-6" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-6" aria-label="Back to reference C-6">↩<sup>6</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-7" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-7" aria-label="Back to reference C-7">↩<sup>7</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-8" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-8" aria-label="Back to reference C-8">↩<sup>8</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-9" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-9" aria-label="Back to reference C-9">↩<sup>9</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-10" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-10" aria-label="Back to reference C-10">↩<sup>10</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-11" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-11" aria-label="Back to reference C-11">↩<sup>11</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-12" data-hash-target to="ability-rogue_talents-ref-C-12" aria-label="Back to reference C-12">↩<sup>12</sup></InnerLink></p>
